          <p><img
              src="data:image/png;base64,"
              alt="condition"> <img
              src="data:image/png;base64,"
              alt="condition"></p>
          <p>These are all the operators for DateTime condition.</p>
          <p>Note that you will need to put &quot;value&quot; always as the correct format &quot;yyyy-MM-dd
